# Enterprise Network Planning

## Objective

Design an enterprise network using Cisco Packet Tracer that demonstrates VLAN implementation, routing, DHCP and network connectivity.

## Departments

- HR
- Finance
- IT

## VLAN Plan

| VLAN | Department | Network |
|------|------------|----------|
|10|HR|192.168.10.0/24|
|20|Finance|192.168.20.0/24|
|30|IT|192.168.30.0/24|

## Expected Outcome

The network will allow devices within different VLANs to communicate through inter-VLAN routing while maintaining logical separation between departments.
